ingredients_text: fructose-glucose syrup, glucose syrup, modified starch, 8% raspberry juice from concentrate, sugar, 2% guava juice from concentrate, acids (citric acid, malic acid, lactic acid), natural flavourings, plant concentrates (black carrot, red cabbage), salt, gelling agent: pectins, hydrolysed pea protein, sunflower oil, glazing agent: carnauba wax (from responsible sources).
